Summary: Mark5 utilities for the DiFX suite
Name: mk5daemon
Version: @version@
Release: 1
License: GPL3
Group: VLBI
BuildRoot: /var/tmp/mk5daemon-@version@-buildroot
Requires: streamstor >= 8.2
Requires: difxmessage >= 2.4.0
Requires: mark5access >= 1.5
Requires: expat
Prefix: /usr
Source: mk5daemon-@version@.tar.gz

%description
Originally this consisted only of several useful utilites for working with Mark5 units.
It has been expanded to become an integral part of the DiFX monitor and control system.

%prep
%setup -q -n mk5daemon-@version@

%build
%configure
make

%install
%makeinstall
chmod a+x /sbin/poweroff
chmod a+x /sbin/reboot
chmod a+x /sbin/halt

%files
%defattr(-,root,root)
%{_bindir}/checkdir
%{_bindir}/fileto5c
%{_bindir}/killjob
%{_bindir}/mk5daemon
%{_bindir}/mk5cat
%{_bindir}/mk5control
%{_bindir}/mk5cp
%{_bindir}/mk5dir
%{_bindir}/mk5erase
%{_bindir}/mk5lock
%{_bindir}/mk5map
%{_bindir}/mk5putdir
%{_bindir}/record5c
%{_bindir}/recover
%{_bindir}/sukill
%{_bindir}/testmod
%{_bindir}/vsn

